entries.journal_entry_description: Deliver the contraband to the fence in the allotted time.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Kam in the allotted time.  For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Lucia in the allotted time.  For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Morris in the allotted time.  For this assignment you must avoid using any methods of travel other than on the ground, the authorities watch the travel terminals and shuttleports like a hawk.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Benton in the allotted time. Benton is located on Yavin 4. For this assignment you will have to launch into space and hyperspace to the Yavin system.  If you try to travel directly using your ship the authorities are sure to catch you.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Deliver the container of contraband to Carter in the allotted time.  Carter is located on Endor. For this assignment you will have to launch into space and hyperspace to the Endor system.  If you try to travel directly using your ship the authorities are sure to catch you.
entries.task07_comm_message_text: This is not good. I deal only with the best. If you cannot handle these assignments I will find someone else who can. Do not fail me again!
